{"tid":957193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士灣仔道鏟上行人路 司機賴路窄","createTime":"2018-12-26T23:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T08:04:20.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"42c713b210e045f40ab3e28918464b76860b1f5a","tid":957193,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T23:46:33.000Z","msg":"凌晨4時25分，一輛空載的士沿灣仔道東行，近活道一個右彎失控，撞向路中安全島及撞毀一支紅綠燈燈柱及燈箱，再衝前30米鏟上左邊行人路，撞毀3米鐵欄及一支消防喉，險撞到一間麵店。<br />\n<br />\n車禍中姓戴64歲司機沒有受傷，他報稱駕駛夜更的士數十年，現場灣仔道雙線雙程行車，他又指路窄以致釀成意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181227/59073743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59073743&d=szw3FXKjsheGnUja62S2fmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a64981ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181227%2F59073743&h=594a0f81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181227/59073743</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c832c0bad1c86eec93e5f4dc02cc6ede0c96dfef","tid":957193,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T23:48:01.000Z","msg":"的士狗講大話過唔到2018<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed3ebb909949628e89558460535b2a38b402b38","tid":957193,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dis